import {Grid, Typography } from "@material-ui/core";
import Box from '@material-ui/core/Box';
import './Login.css';

function Login(){
    return(
      <Grid container >
        <Grid xs={6}>
          <Box component="span">
            <form>
              <Typography >
                Entrar
              </Typography>
            </form>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      
    );
};

export default Login;
